{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/indistopia-kostum-komik-haryadhi/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Indistopia: Komik Sindiran Untuk Netizen Indonesia","content":"<p>Pernah membayangkan apa yang terjadi jika suatu hari dunia menjadi terbalik? Bayangkan jika setiap hari adalah hari kebalikan, atau tiba-tiba seisi dunia menjadi dunia Bizarro dari dunia DC Comics. Percaya nggak percaya, inilah yang dialami Giwi dalam komik Indistopia.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52679\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52679\" data-attachment-id=\"52679\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/indistopia-kostum-komik-haryadhi/attachment/01-indistopia/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/01-indistopia.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-indistopia\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/01-indistopia-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/01-indistopia.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52679\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/01-indistopia.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/01-indistopia.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/01-indistopia-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52679\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Suatu ketika, Giwi bertemu dengan dukun yang konon bisa membuka portal ke dimensi lain. Karena Giwi meremehkan kemampuannya, sang dukung langsung saja menunjukkan kemampuannya dengan melempar Giwi ke dimensi lain. Begitu sadar, Giwi awalnya nggak melihat perbedaan dengan dunia yang awalnya ia tinggali. Namun, orang-orang di dunia itu bertingkah aneh dan terbalik dari biasanya!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52680\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52680\" data-attachment-id=\"52680\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/indistopia-kostum-komik-haryadhi/attachment/02-indistopia/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/02-indistopia.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-indistopia\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/02-indistopia-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/02-indistopia.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52680\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/02-indistopia.jpg\" alt=\"indistopia\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/02-indistopia.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/02-indistopia-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52680\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Giwi merasakan sendiri bagaimana para polisi justru menilang pejalan kaki yang mengganggu premotor di trotoar. Dia dilayani ketus oleh pelayan warteg yang malas menyiapkan makanan. Bahkan Giwi juga dikejar-kejar massa karena dia nggak memberikan uang yang banyak untuk pengamen! Giwi kini harus bertahan hidup dalam dimensi Indistopia: dimana Indonesia ditinggali oleh masyarakat yang tingkahnya sangat buruk!</p>\n<p>Kalau kamu akrab dengan komik <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/KOSTUMKOMIK\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Kostum</a>, kamu juga pasti bakal langsung akrab dengan Indistopia. Komik Kostum bikinan Haryadhi ini sejak awal memang dikenal dengan kontennya yang senantiasa menggelitik para pembaca, secara halus maupun frontal. Aktif berkarya di media sosial, kini Haryadhi melebarkan sayap Kostum ke platform komik lokal CIAYO Comics lewat Indistopia.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga:Â <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/komik-anak-bangsa-di-media-sosial/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">17 Komik Anak Bangsa yang Berhasil Mewarnai Media Sosial Milenial Indonesia</a></strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52681\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52681\" data-attachment-id=\"52681\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/indistopia-kostum-komik-haryadhi/attachment/03-indistopia/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/03-indistopia.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-indistopia\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/03-indistopia-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/03-indistopia.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52681\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/03-indistopia.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/03-indistopia.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/03-indistopia-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52681\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Di dalam Indistopia, Haryadhi nggak memperhalus pesan-pesan yang disampaikan di sini. Sindiran-sindiran tajam dilontarkan lewat sosok masyarakat Indistopia yang merupakan representasi buruk dari sifat-sifat bermasyarakat. Bacalah dua tiga episode komik ini dan bayangkan. Siapa tahu kamu pernah melakukan hal-hal yang muncul di sana?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52682\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52682\" data-attachment-id=\"52682\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/indistopia-kostum-komik-haryadhi/attachment/04-indistopia/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/04-indistopia.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-indistopia\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/04-indistopia-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/04-indistopia.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52682\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/04-indistopia.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/04-indistopia.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/04-indistopia-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52682\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Haryadhi nampaknya ingin memberi pesan kepada pembaca, bahwa kemajuan negara Indonesia tidak hanya bergantung kepada pemerintah, namun masyarakatnya juga. Keduanya harus saling bersinergi untuk mewujudkan kehidupan bernegara yang tentram. Namun jika salah satu atau keduanya tidak berfungsi sebagaimana mestinya, maka bukan tidak mungkin Indistopia yang hadir dalam komik ini menjadi kenyataan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52683\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52683\" data-attachment-id=\"52683\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/indistopia-kostum-komik-haryadhi/attachment/05-indistopia/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/05-indistopia.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-indistopia\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/05-indistopia-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/05-indistopia.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52683\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/05-indistopia.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/05-indistopia.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/05-indistopia-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52683\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Penasaran dengan kelanjutan kisah Giwi? Gimana cara dia kembali ke dimensi normal? Pernah ngerasain kejadian yang sama dengan Giwi, atau justru kamu punya pengalaman serupa dengan para penduduk Indistopia? Ikuti terus komik Indistopia, setiap hari Rabu pukul 19:00 WIB, di CIAYO Comics! Kamu juga bisa cek komik <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/genre/comedy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">komedi</a> dan <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/genre/slice-of-life\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">slice of life</a> lainnya di CIAYO Comics.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"7c19044f-a611-50bb-803a-1b114499ef9a"}}}